\q out came all the nobles left,
\q out for the Eternal marched his folk like heroes,
\q
\v 14 wheeling from Ephraim into the glen—
\q “We follow you, Benjamin, your clan’s men!”
\q Out from Machir came commanders,
\q adjutants from Zebulun;
\q
